reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.md:70:- If: The practice helps achievement-contingent overinterpreters. Then: Stable participants using Return Without Verdict show fewer worth verdicts, shame swings, certainty inflation, and post-state rumination than ordinary journaling or rest-and-plan controls. Weakens if: The practice increases rumination, derealization, shame, dependency, avoidance, or performs no better than controls. Test surface: Two-week pilot with screened self-directed practitioners, students, caregivers, and professionals high in perfectionism or achievement-contingent self-worth.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.md:81:- Burnout clinicians or coaches working with perfectionism
