reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-time-is-up-not-when-it-feels-done-4b185ee8c360296e.md:72:- If: The benefit is moderated by failure mode. Then: High-rumination and high-perfectionism participants benefit more than under-reflectors, grievers, and avoidant participants. Weakens if: The timer helps equally across groups, or mainly helps by ordinary scheduling rather than by reducing compulsive resolution seeking. Test surface: Moderator analysis comparing over-reflection, avoidance, grief, and perfectionism profiles.
