observations/codex/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return.md:89:The three-box completion model was weakened by MN 22, Heart Sutra reliance, Rinzai curriculum, Dogen practice-realization, authority-boundary prior art, and modern perfectionism and burnout pressure. The surviving teaching is narrower: test the return, not the peak.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-audit-you-cannot-hold-alone-f39d5f3ff774b3f9.md:30:Secondary literature gap: Before publication, read full work on scrupulosity, OCD reassurance seeking, family or clergy accommodation, intolerance of uncertainty, spiritual direction ethics, VCE meditation-related challenges, achievement-contingent self-worth, perfectionism, behavioral activation, and spiritual abuse. The strongest source gap is whether bounded relational custody can be separated empirically from reassurance accommodation.
