./runs/20260530-091655-codex-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/codex-cli.stderr.log:2472:    "confidence_effect": "Prevents candidate-discovery status. The model is useful as a heuristic only if it can code no-threshold, no-peak, Other Power, inherited practice, and practice-realization without forcing them into a modern after-experience frame.",
./runs/20260530-091655-codex-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/codex-cli.stderr.log:2473:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "These cases resist the sequence of method, result, and return. Dogen makes practice and realization inseparable. Tannisho relocates efficacy to Amida's Vow and can make nembutsu non-practice from the practitioner's side. Inherited religion may not have a discrete completion event. Ordinary ethical formation may return without peak experience at all."
./runs/20260530-091655-codex-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/codex-cli.stderr.log:2479:    "Different primary texts model different endings: MN 22 releases the raft after right use, Heart Sutra negates attainment while retaining reliance, Mandukya allows a known Self, Rinzai koan work exhausts ordinary thinking while remaining curriculum, and Dogen collapses before and after through practice-realization.",
