./runs/20260530-091655-codex-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/codex-cli.stderr.log:2540:      "overlap": "Close anomaly and near-neighbor. Dogen's practice-realization already says practice is not a means to a later result and realization is not an object privately recognized after practice.",
