./runs/20260530-091655-codex-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/codex-cli.stderr.log:2573:    "Close-read Tannisho, Dogen Bendowa or Genjokoan, a Rinzai koan curriculum source, Cloud of Unknowing or Dionysius, a Dzogchen pointing-out source, and one Sufi fana or baqa source before raising source reliability."
./runs/20260530-091655-codex-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/codex-cli.stderr.log:2575:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.58 to 0.41. The teaching line is strong and publishable only as a restrained synthesis for achievement-contingent self-worth. The research model should be treated as extended prior art until it predicts warnings, repairs, or return duties better than existing upaya, raft, apophatic, practice-realization, spiritual-exercises, VCE, authority, and grammar frameworks.",
